'''塞尔维亚-西班牙关系'''是[[塞尔维亚|塞尔维亚]]和[[西班牙|西班牙]]之间的外交关系。两国于1916年10月14日建立了外交关系。<ref name="Bilateralni-odnosi-Španija">{{Cite news |url=http://www.mfa.gov.rs/sr/index.php/spoljna-politika/bilateralni-odnosi/117-bilateralni-odnosi/11563-spanija?lang=lat |title=Bilateralni odnosi-Španija |access-date=1 June 2018 |publisher=[[塞尔维亚共和国外交部|塞尔维亚共和国外交部]] |archive-date=2015-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150204130641/http://www.mfa.gov.rs/sr/index.php/spoljna-politika/bilateralni-odnosi/117-bilateralni-odnosi/11563-spanija?lang=lat |dead-url=yes }}</ref>塞尔维亚在[[马德里|马德里]]设有大使馆，西班牙在[[贝尔格莱德|贝尔格莱德]]设有大使馆。这两个国家都是[[联合国|联合国]]、[[国际刑警组织|国际刑警组织]]、[[欧洲理事会|欧洲理事会]]和[[欧洲安全与合作组织|欧洲安全与合作组织]]的成员国。西班牙自1986年起成为欧盟成员国，塞尔维亚自2012年起成为候选国家，西班牙强烈支持塞尔维亚加入欧盟。<ref name="EuropeanWB">{{Cite news |url=http://europeanwesternbalkans.rs/dacic-spanija-najcvrsce-podrzava-srbiju-u-eu/ |title=Dačić: Španija najčvršće podržava Srbiju u EU |date=2 November 2011 |access-date=1 June 2018 |publisher=EWB |archive-date=2019-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524230515/https://europeanwesternbalkans.rs/dacic-spanija-najcvrsce-podrzava-srbiju-u-eu/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>西班牙是[[北约|北约]]成员国，塞尔维亚是军事中立国，与[[不结盟运动|不结盟运动]]有着密切的历史关系。

西班牙是不承认科索沃单方面宣布独立的五个欧盟成员国之一，并积极反对科索沃加入联合国教科文组织和国际刑警组织等国际组织。<ref name="RSE-5-EU-Kosovo">{{Cite news |url=https://www.slobodnaevropa.org/a/kosovo_koci_nepriznavanje_pet_clanica_eu/24379515.html |title=Nepriznavanje pet članica EU koči Kosovo |last=Zejneli Loxha |first=Amra |date=2 November 2011 |access-date=1 June 2018 |publisher=[[自由欧洲电台／自由电台|自由欧洲电台／自由电台]] |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129024052/https://www.slobodnaevropa.org/a/kosovo_koci_nepriznavanje_pet_clanica_eu/24379515.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="La Oficina de Información Diplomática">{{Cite news |url=http://www.exteriores.gob.es/Documents/FichasPais/SERBIA_FICHA%20PAIS.pdf |format=PDF |title=Ficha país Serbia; La Oficina de Información Diplomática |date=March 2018 |access-date=7 June 2018 |publisher=[[西班牙外交及合作部|西班牙外交及合作部]] |language=es |archive-date=2020-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605062957/http://www.exteriores.gob.es/Documents/FichasPais/SERBIA_FICHA%20PAIS.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>此外，西班牙支持塞尔维亚坚持按照2013年在欧盟主持下签署的《[[2013年布魯塞爾協定|布鲁塞尔协议]]》的规定，在科索沃建立塞尔维亚自治社区。<ref name="ATVBL">{{Cite news |url=http://www.atvbl.com/spanija-eu-da-podrzi-formiranje-zso/ |title=Španija: EU da podrži formiranje ZSO |date=14 April 2018 |access-date=1 June 2018 |publisher=ATBL |archive-date=2019-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524230456/https://www.atvbl.com/spanija-eu-da-podrzi-formiranje-zso |dead-url=no }}</ref>一些人解释了西班牙对科索沃的强硬立场，将其内部问题与加泰罗尼亚独立运动以及联合王国在直布罗陀的争端相提并论。在[[2017年加泰罗尼亚独立公投|2017年加泰罗尼亚独立公投]]危机期间，塞尔维亚强烈支持西班牙的领土完整，塞尔维亚外交部长表示，西班牙是塞尔维亚最好的国际朋友之一。<ref name="Blic-2017-Katalonija">{{Cite news |url=https://www.blic.rs/vesti/politika/dacic-o-referendumu-u-kataloniji-srbija-podrzava-celovitost-spanije/94wqvf8 |title=Dačić o referendumu u Kataloniji: Srbija podržava celovitost Španije |date=1 October 2017 |access-date=1 June 2018 |publisher=Blic |archive-date=2019-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524230456/https://www.blic.rs/vesti/politika/dacic-o-referendumu-u-kataloniji-srbija-podrzava-celovitost-spanije/94wqvf8 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

作为第三方，两国都支持阿根廷在其与英国的福克兰群岛主权争端中的立场。<ref name="MFA-ARG-2017">{{Cite news |url=http://www.mfa.gov.rs/en/press-service/statements/17203-argentina-to-maintain-its-principled-position-to-adhere-to-international-law-supporting-the-territorial-integrity-of-serbia |title=Argentina to maintain its principled position to adhere to international law, supporting the territorial integrity of Serbia |date=22 November 2017 |access-date=2 June 2018 |publisher=[[塞尔维亚共和国外交部|塞尔维亚共和国外交部]] |archive-date=2019-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524230456/http://www.mfa.gov.rs/en/press-service/statements/17203-argentina-to-maintain-its-principled-position-to-adhere-to-international-law-supporting-the-territorial-integrity-of-serbia |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="MercoPress-Argentina-Spain">{{Cite news |url=http://en.mercopress.com/2016/04/05/argentina-and-spain-agree-to-re-launch-closer-political-and-trade-relations |title=Argentina and Spain agree to re-launch closer political and trade relations |date=5 April 2016 |access-date=2 June 2018 |publisher=[[MercoPress|MercoPress]] |archive-date=2019-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524230455/https://en.mercopress.com/2016/04/05/argentina-and-spain-agree-to-re-launch-closer-political-and-trade-relations |dead-url=no }}</ref>
